description: This file contains DTO (Data Transfer Object) classes used for note operations in a note management system, including create, update requests, and response structures.

classes.name: NoteDtos
classes.description: Container class for note-related DTOs, including request and response classes.

classes.name: CreateRequest
classes.description: DTO for creating a new note, containing title and content.

classes.name: UpdateRequest
classes.description: DTO for updating an existing note, including optional archived flag.

classes.name: NoteResponse
classes.description: DTO representing the note data sent back in responses, including metadata such as timestamps and UUID.
